  1. [Story title from Task 1.1]
  2. [Story title from Task 1.3]
  3. [Story title from Task 2.1]
  ...

VS2: [Descriptive Name]
Goal: [Specific measurable outcome]
Stories (Count: [N]):
  1. [Story title from Task 1.2]
  2. [Story title from Task 2.2]
  ...

VS3: [Descriptive Name]
Goal: [Specific measurable outcome]
Stories (Count: [N]):
  1. [Story title from Task 3.1]
  2. [Story title from Task 3.2]
  ...
```

