**Options**:
- "Approve all - Create all stories in Jira (VS1, VS2, VS3)"
- "Approve VS1 only - Create only VS1 stories in Jira"
- "Request changes - Provide feedback on the story map first"

**If PM requests changes:**
- Listen to feedback
- Update the story map document
- Re-present for approval
- Iterate until approved

**If PM approves:**
- Proceed to handoff to 430-story-writing
- Note which value slices were approved (all, or VS1 only, etc.)
- Pass the approved value slice filter to 430

